Program: Free Thinking
Title: Martin Amis in Conversation at the BBC Proms
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04h7vtp
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 17 Sep 2014
Martin Amis's 14th novel The Zone of Interest sees him return to the topic of the Holocaust for the first time since his controversial book Time's Arrow. He discusses his writing with Philip Dodd in a conversation recorded in front of an audience at the Royal College of Music last month as a Proms Plus Literary Event. Show less